Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the snow didn't fall for very long.{it quickly stopped falling}{I guess it's accurate, then....}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.48,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the sea god is angry.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.67,0:04:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad better not be drinking like a fish{bwahaha} or skipping meals just 'cause I'm not there to stop him.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, what's he been doing about food since I left?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.65,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning. What're you up to?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.14,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trying to figure out how to go about fixing this.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.47,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you guys doing here so early anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say we were thrown out.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.34,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All the adults said they had \Nan important meeting to attend
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we should head to school early.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A meeting?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it has something to do with \Nthe saltflake snow falling on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, adults always do stuff like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep everything a secret from us just 'cause we're kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we've got the Wooden Maiden!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're the ones in charge of the Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.26,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us really want to see this through to the end.
