Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay with you too, right, {replace}Teach{Sensei}?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids...
