Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure it's a success no matter what!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time,{ once we're done,} I'm definitely treating you all to ramen{ after}!{pls no}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps said we could borrow this.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda thought it'd be bigger, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to repainting it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should reinforce it first.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for letting us borrow this.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kinda overdoing it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do that?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Loosen up, or you're gonna hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.49,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it might be time you all took a break for lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I volunteer to go make us something!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some things from Saya Mart first!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not be doing this just so you can buy a snack for yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.66,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I'm gonna support her.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're gonna get fat, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari's really trying hard...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't say that!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so heavy.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll help.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys came too!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.03,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,behold my awesome creation.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't drop it, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the hip microwave! You can count on us!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.31,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there {replace}dumplings{shumai} in it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what everyone would like...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Manaka{-chan}?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.13,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hi, Akari{-san}!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably go with something that'll keep you warm.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.61,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer's been a bit chilly.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something warm and from the sea...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, has Hikari said anything?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, about the sea or home or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess maybe he's not worried about Dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He is!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.57,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun} really {\i1}is{\i0} worried about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They both care so much for each other,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet things are going so badly...{they both care for each other, yet the divide between the two seems unbridgable}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, can I please use your—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu often knocked that over when he first came here.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"When he first came here"?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu{-kun} hasn't always lived here?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He came here on his own when he was nine.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How come he came on his own?{shes asking after the circumstances, not his motivation}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, his parents live{d} in the city.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu{-kun} came here all by himself...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.63,0:09:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So even when he was little, \NTsumugu{-kun} was just the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.94,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought to myself
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.96,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that Tsumugu{-kun}'s really good at finding himself and seeing things others can't.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he found his love for the sea \Nwhen he was little, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.92,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's why he chose to come here...{technically should be a colon followed by a lowercase "because," but that just looks weird.}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he knows...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he knows what's precious to him!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya know? Everyone says \NCafé Triangle is the place for meets.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Meats?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get{mince} meat there?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.08,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place where guys and girls are friendly with each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like your mouth's working just fine, \Nbut how about your hands?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They're working too!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. That's good.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna do even more, and then—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.57,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm gonna go back to school to get some tools, so can you \Ncheck if{whether} there's wood in the back to reinforce the boat?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm counting on you little ladies.{what a pimp}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished, so I can help you girls paint.{might be a little long, so take out the first clause. "let me help you paint"}{timing's fine (Devana made me say it)}
