Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We did an awesome job{ of painting}! What do you—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Chisaki? Did she go somewhere?{asshole, you're supposed to notice how she painted it nicely}{He can't help that he's a pimp.}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.94,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for earlier.{shes grateful he ~cares~}{I'm just gonna leave what CR had, then.}
