Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"How come?"
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone else is changing, so I have to change too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what "change" means to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.34,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that what it means to become an adult?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just keep thinking about yourself!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So {\i1}that's{\i0} why you're neglecting your feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.04,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't forgive yourself for the way you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu{-kun}, what...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the way you are{ right now} is just fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.73,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki! What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling well, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.57,0:12:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.37,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand him!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's the reason you look so upset...{uh... he's the one giving you that long face? he's the reason you look that ........}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The village...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different somehow.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you still need this?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It took me a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already done for the day.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd Chisaki and Kaname go?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They went home already.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.16,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they had something to do...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Smells like the food's ready.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, {replace}those are the dumplings that go{that's the shumai that goes} inside the wooden microwave.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.98,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Be careful with that!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how hard I worked on that thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That smells good.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's soup with seafood and pork!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mixing seafood and pork is just plain wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.54,0:14:31.32,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{Yum!}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.96,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be nice if things from the sea and things from the surface got along.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.09,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea and the surface...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was payback for making my knees buckle earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's completely different!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.77,0:15:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For a lot of reasons...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Hii{-kun},
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.55,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here right now because you were there for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for always being there for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you getting so serious all of a—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.47,0:15:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,People feel more confident with somebody by their side{s}.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've taught me so much, Hii{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're friends, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.47,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's hard for you to go back home, I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I need—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.49,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more confident with you by my side. \NI'm sure your dad feels the same way I do!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.68,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,could become stronger if you told him you care about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be{come} happier!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.79,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...{.} What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd support her...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think I can control myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.02,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom? Dad?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.10,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, you can't go to the surface anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
