Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka's your friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your {\i1}friend{\i0}, you idiot.{TLC I hope it's okay. You usually sometimes say derogatory things to yourself when trying to snap yourself back to reality, after all.}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.95,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, if you'd please \Nopen your textbooks to page 48—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.87,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I couldn't sleep too well last night...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like at least Hikari made it today.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.20,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the other Shioshishio kids showed up for class.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.04,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to contact them, \Nbut I couldn't reach them.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know if something happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.57,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys are trying to \Nstop the Boatdrift Ceremony again!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.53,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go{ back} to the village \Nand settle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.41,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna tell 'em!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.74,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna tell all those old guys {\i0}and{\i1} Dad—every one of 'em!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where {\i1}is{\i0} everyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did something happen to the village?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come back.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's hurry and go see {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do I have to go see {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, I said!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, we told you not to leave the house!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.39,0:19:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I left, the village has completely{TLC changed, I'm assuming. We might want to make this a full sentence for the batch.}...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got home last night,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there were a lot of adults waiting for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They told me I couldn't go up to the surface anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad wouldn't even let me out of the house.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to go up to the surface?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what they said when I got back.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Why'd they say that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it was dangerous on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They said the same thing to Chii{-chan} and Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They said none of us could leave the village.{The repetition of this "They said" is intentional here.}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then why would you come outside by yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I had to tell you, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though we both care about each other...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manaka's feelings are different from mine.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even so...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I came out here...{I like this repetition, too. When you cry, you repeat yourself, after all.}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't help how I feel.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because I just had to tell you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.69,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.98,0:21:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home.{why don't any of them just swim up}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen on the surface?
