Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is getting more and more gray...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.50,0:23:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The humans will forget the sea god...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of humans themselves...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:36.26,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The humans will not be able to bear the cold that is about to come.
